{"tid":2429082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"氣候公義彰顯！法國氣候訴訟勝利！","createTime":"2021-03-02T05:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T12:23:55.000Z","uid":74339,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0c759738a26c4fb0b525f526fa367ffa7bd07f00","tid":2429082,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:04:24.000Z","msg":"2021年2月3日巴黎行政法院作出的判決，為氣候公義建立里程碑！就一宗氣候訴訟，法庭宣判，包括綠色和平法國辦公室在內的原告勝訴，法國政府須對氣候危機負有責任。成果背後，感謝230萬人聯署支持，這是法國史上最多人參與的線上聯署，「世紀訴訟」的報捷，可以說公義站於氣候與人民的一方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.greenpeace.org/hongkong/issues/climate/update/25999/氣候公義彰顯！法國氣候訴訟勝利！/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenpeace.org%2Fhongkong%2Fissues%2Fclimate%2Fupdate%2F25999%2F%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%A9%E5%BD%B0%E9%A1%AF%EF%BC%81%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%B0%A3%E5%80%99%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E5%8B%9D%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%81%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=c6bf4234\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.greenpeace.org/hongkong/issues/climate/update/25999/氣候公義彰顯！法國氣候訴訟勝利！/</a>"},{"pid":"ceda9cd9a48a3cbddba35cd945057aa23226e036","tid":2429082,"uid":60057,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"全世界一齊執支那啲屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bedd69be3deeef861205640aad5033695d1c0fe","tid":2429082,"uid":74339,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"你太憎支那搞到唔能夠公正咁睇個問題 啲屎係一百五十年前歐美工業化帶落嚟 而且到今日都仲未解決<br />\n<br />\n支那當然有問題 但絕對唔係最主要"},{"pid":"81732d4db81ccb4d84b956be5d9038773ea42a43","tid":2429082,"uid":55951,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2bedd69be3deeef861205640aad5033695d1c0fe","tid":2429082,"uid":74339,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"你太憎支那搞到唔能夠公正咁睇個問題 啲屎係一百五十年前歐美工業化帶落嚟 而且到今日都仲未解決<br />\n<br />\n支那當然有問題 但絕對唔係最主要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:12:07.000Z","msg":"咁點解支那唔需要負責？"},{"pid":"419df85